{"tid":1464240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪應該將和你飛令旅客滯留的責任俾翻政府？","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:46:25.000Z","uid":111235,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a67cb70514e235f3457cee6776f941e94cbdbfe4","tid":1464240,"uid":111235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"今日係機場同滯留旅客對話<br />\n發現佢地好正常地將個責任spin咗去示威者到 而唔係政府<br />\n即使本身支持五大訴求的人都會覺得好無奈 唔知可以點 無了期等待<br />\n我地係咪應該要set翻個deadline俾政府 要政府正面回應五大訴求？<br />\nspin翻個責任去政府到 等旅客都有個等待的心 覺得要由政府去解決個問題. <br />\n到時假設政府唔回應，都係政府的問題"},{"pid":"7bc0e1dbc0009d88fbd60a8280d6114fc5fa766d","tid":1464240,"uid":3553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/jkERqOR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkERqOR.gif&h=a819dc48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c6c6d3c69a97c4973cbc92fea26c120284c3793","tid":1464240,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"推 政府搞到咁"},{"pid":"0544ab1bfeef51a092ed2f97ae5ab83aa01f3ce6","tid":1464240,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"同意，要做到人太多我哋都唔想<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"5f8f215776b682bf80196239666542ebb407f90f","tid":1464240,"uid":111235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"塞機場唔係唔得 但都要顧旅客感受 <br />\n同真係要塞翻個責任俾政府"},{"pid":"6bec0c36761758e47855864b7f